  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Squeeze the <strong>sausage</strong><strong>meat</strong> out of their casings directly into the pan</p>\r\n<p>Cook for 5 min until the <strong>sausagemeat</strong> is brown and crispy, breaking it up into small pieces with a wooden spoon as you go&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-and-leek-sausage-bolognese/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Peel the <strong>onion</strong><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, <strong>carrot</strong><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> and <strong>garlic</strong></p>\r\n<p>Grate the <strong>onion</strong><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, <strong>carrot</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span>, <strong>garlic</strong> and <strong>mushrooms</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tip: alternatively bung everything in a food processor for speedier results!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-and-leek-sausage-bolognese/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add all of the <strong>grated</strong> <strong>vegetables</strong> to the pan</p>\r\n<p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\r\n<p>Cook for 4 min until soft and caramelised</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-and-leek-sausage-bolognese/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>linguine</strong>&nbsp;to a pot of boiled water with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 8-12 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, drain and reserve 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> of the <strong>starchy pasta&nbsp;<strong>water</strong></strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-and-leek-sausage-bolognese/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, stir the <strong>brown</strong> <strong>sauce</strong>, <strong>tomato</strong> <strong>paste</strong>, <strong>dried</strong>&nbsp;<strong>basil</strong> and <strong>dried</strong>&nbsp;<strong>oregano</strong>&nbsp;into the pan&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cook for 1 min further&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-and-leek-sausage-bolognese/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> and season with a generous pinch of <strong>sugar</strong></p>\r\n<p>Tip: the sugar&nbsp;balances the acidity of the&nbsp;tomatoes</p>\r\n<p>Cook for 6 min or until the sauce has thickened to a bolognese consistency</p>\r\n<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-and-leek-sausage-bolognese/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the drained <strong>linguine</strong>&nbsp;into the sauce, along with the reserved <strong>pasta</strong> <strong>water</strong>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Taste for seasoning, adding more&nbsp;<strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>if needed</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pork-and-leek-sausage-bolognese/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the bolognese and garnish with the cheese</p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
